{% macro render_ci_integration(language) -%}
##### CI Integration

{% if language == 'python' -%}
```yaml
# GitHub Actions example
- name: Run tests
  run: pytest --cov --cov-branch --cov-report=xml

- name: Mutation tests
  run: |
    pip install mutmut
    mutmut run
    mutmut html > mutation_report.html
```

{% elif language == 'typescript' -%}
```yaml
# GitHub Actions example
- name: Run tests
  run: pnpm vitest run --coverage

- name: Mutation tests
  run: |
    pnpm add -D @stryker-mutator/core
    npx stryker run
```

